         This

        site was created by Mr. Ferwerda in

        order to help his Chemistry students at 
         Tecumseh

        High School   

         in Tecumseh,

        Michigan. All chemistry students are welcome and I hope it will be helpful. The text that corresponds to the chapters

        listed at this site is Chemistry, 2008 edition, by

        Wilbraham et al, published by Prentice-Hall.

         
          

   

                                        
